A live 1975 Led Zeppelin compilation I put together some years ago.  I've enjoyed it and thought others might enjoy it as well.  It's more or less merged together to give the impression of a long three hour 45 minute concert.  Mostly using Earls Court '75, New York '75 and Vancouver '75 with a couple other tracks thrown in.  I went with some of the better sounding recordings.

Feel free to share with anyone anytime anywhere.
Seed if possible. Thanks, Mike
